posts.description:
No makeup, no problem 🥰 despite all the travel (from winter to summer climates), crazy work scheds and hormonal breakouts (ladies, you feel me 🙋🏽‍♀️) I'm soooo happy and confident with my skin!
All the credit goes to @belobeauty 💞
So happy to be back for a pamper day! 😌 Well overdue! @victoria_belo @dochayden
#BeloBeauty

I looove a productive day 💯 Paid my bills, bought stuff online, paid my share for a group gift - all done with BDO Pay ✅💳💸! Super easy to use (I just used my friend's phone number in my contacts to send her money!) 😊 If you have a BDO Digital Banking account, you can already use BDO Pay with the same login ASAP! 👍 Try it out and tell me what you think! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ #BDOPay

Last na to' ☺ Final look for #BinibiningPilipinas2021 🌷

Also shout out to my co-host and sister queen @binibiningnicolecordoves ! I'm soooo proud to see you host BBP as a main host after 2 years!! 😍 Sharing the stage with you is so much fun, when kaya yung next?!

Again thank you to my team for all my looks! It's definitely a challenge logistically traveling with the aspect of quarantine and trying to prepare! But we found ways haha Love you guyssss 🤗🤗🤗

Late post cause I crashed last night, but a huge congratulations is in order for our new 🇵🇭 @bbpilipinasofficial queens!!!!
So excited to witness your journeys! Bring home the crowns! 👑

Captured by @noel_cantalejo

February 5, 2020 was the afternoon I met up with Madam Stella and in-between catching up, I floated the idea of an all-female hosting tandem for a future edition.
To now to be getting ready to host Binibining Pilipinas 2021 @bbpilipinasofficial along side my sister queen @binibiningnicolecordoves and to be celebrating my third official year with Binibini hits different 🥺.
Always and forever grateful for the guidance and opportunities Madam Stella has given me...from the chance to represent our beautiful country at @missuniverse 🇵🇭 now to be present as a mentor and host for BBP2021. 🙏
Philippines, our girls this year are incredible. They are fighters - true testaments that Filipinas are women who fight for their dreams.
Support them tonight, 9:30PM for the show! Streaming on @bbpilipinasofficial YouTube channel and on Kapamilya, A2Z, Metro and IWantTFC Channels. ⚡
